  "instructions": [
    "Heat a large Dutch oven over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the beef and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the pork sausage and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the onion, carrots, and potatoes, and cook until the vegetables are tender, about 10 minutes.",
    "Add the turmeric, sea salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add 2 cups of water to the pot and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 30 minutes.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh parsley if desired."
